      AST-2014-004
    </uri>
    <uri link="http://nvd.nist.gov/nvd.cfm?cvename=CVE-2014-2286">CVE-2014-2286</uri>
    <uri link="http://nvd.nist.gov/nvd.cfm?cvename=CVE-2014-2287">CVE-2014-2287</uri>
